'<br><br>If you hand him Washed Blasted Stone:<br><br>Targen Stonefall says 'Thank you. This will make a nice trinket for my son's rock collection.'<br>You receive 1 platinum from Targen Stonefall.<br><br>Adiase</p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
